GripPosition: Vector representing an object being held in the player's hand
GripRotation: Quaternion representing an object being held in the player's hand
AimPosition: For handheld controllers, gives a vector for pointing at objects
AimRotation: For handheld controllers, gives a quaternion for pointing at objects
PalmPosition: For handheld controllers, gives a vector for representing the hand
PalmRotation: For handheld controllers, gives a quaternion for representing the hand
HandKeyPositions: The indices of this array are the values of EHandKeypoint (Palm, Wrist, ThumbMetacarpal, etc).
HandKeyRotations: The indices of this array are the values of EHandKeypoint (Palm, Wrist, ThumbMetacarpal, etc).
HandKeyRadii: The indices of this array are the values of EHandKeypoint (Palm, Wrist, ThumbMetacarpal, etc).
